oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Passport 1909
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A passport was issued to Sarah Alice Lowe on May 8, 1909. Good for two years from the date of issuance, an in depth physical description was provided because no picture was shown. 11 x 17 in.
